name: Cypherdog Token
description: CDOG is a proprietary deflationary token made for maximum efficiency and utility. It was built on the Polygon network to ensure that the project is scalable and that all interested parties can participate. The introduction of the CDOG token in January 2022 was an important milestone for Cypherdog. Since September 13, 2022, the Cypherdog Token, CDOG, is live and can be traded on BitMart.
